title: GOVERNOR’S OFFICE NEWS RELEASE: State’s Bond Outlook improves rating, paving way for Ige administration’s first ...
text: ( Source : The Office of the Governor of the State of Hawaii ) (HONOLULU) - Governor Ige's office today announced that Moody's Investors Service ( Moody 's) improved the outlook on its rating of State of Hawaii general obligation ( G.O. ) bonds
